Problem Statement : Given 3 numbers A, B and C. Find the greatest number among them.
Solution (C++) : 
class Solution {
  public:
    int greatestOfThree(int A, int B, int C) {
        if(A>B && A>C)
            return A;
        else if(B>C && B>A)
            return B;
        else if(C>A && C>B)
            return C;
    }
};
Explanation :To find the greatest among the given 3 numbers we use if..else..if.. conditions.
If one of the number is greater than the other two numbers,then that number is returned.
